title: Qualified with April Beyer Episode 6
itunes:title: Qualified with April Beyer Episode 6
description:
Matchmaker, relationship coach and CEO of LEVEL connections, April Beyer is back as Anna’s more qualified co-host in this special episode. 


This episode is all about moving on from heartbreak and figuring out when to start dating again. Anna and April’s first call is with Stephanie who broke up with her partner of fifteen years. While she’s confident that ending things was the right decision, Stephanie finds herself missing the relationship and feeling unsure of where to go from here. 


Next, is a conversation with Jen who had just gotten engaged to the love of her life when he confessed that he had cheated. After spending 10 long months trying to repair the relationship, it was over. Now Jen finds herself dating a man who offers everything she ever wanted but she still can’t stop herself from comparing him to her ex. 


Learn more about April and LEVEL by visiting www.levelconnections.com


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
